<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6457439>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–7. Mongoloraphidia xinjiangana sp. nov., holotype male. 1. Habitus, dorsal view; 2. Photograph of genitalia, lateral view; 3. Photograph of hypandrium internum; 4. Photograph of genitalia, ventral view; 5. Line drawing of genitalia, lateral view; 6. Line drawing of hypandrium internum; 7. Line drawing of genitalia, ventral view. A1–A2: anal veins; CuA: cubitus anterior; CuP: cubitus posterior; MA: media anterior; MP: media posterior; RA: radius anterior; RP: radius posterior; Sc, subcosta; C: costa; e: ectoproct; ep: endophallus; gp9: gonapophyses 9 (hypovalva); gst9: gonostylus 9; gx9: gonocoxite 9; S8, 9: sternum 8 and 9; T8, 9: tergum 8 and 9. Scale bar = 1.0 mm (1), 0.5 mm (2–7)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6457439/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6457441>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–12. Mongoloraphidia (Mongoloraphidia) kaszabi (H. Aspöck & U. Aspöck, 1967), male. 8. Habitus, dorsal view; 9. Photograph of genitalia, lateral view; 10. Photograph of genitalia, caudal view; 11. Photograph of hypandrium internum; 12. Photograph of genitalia, ventral view. A1–A2: anal veins; CuA: cubitus anterior; CuP: cubitus posterior; MA: media anterior; MP: media posterior; RA: radius anterior; RP: radius posterior; Sc, subcosta; C: costa; e: ectoproct; ep: endophallus; gp9: gonapophyses 9 (hypovalva); gst9: gonostylus 9; gx9: gonocoxite 9; gx11: gonocoxite 11 (gonarcus); S8, 9: sternum 8 and 9; T8, 9: tergum 8 and 9. Scale bar = 1.0 mm (8), 0.5 mm (9–12)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6457441/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

